: 5px;">A claim on $10 in a bank account, plus</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-b=
ottom: 5px;">The right to pay that $10 to buy a share of some company to be=
 named later.</li></ol><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The median value of Ite=
